{"tid":1744024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門下月正式實施《網絡安全法》","createTime":"2019-11-21T13:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T14:11:27.000Z","uid":173617,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e43da275156c4a81ae460ca22ba83c30583326e8","tid":1744024,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"【#商業熱話】澳門下月正式實施《網絡安全法》<br />\n<br />\n澳門特區《網絡安全法》將在下月22日開始實施，手提電話用戶要實名登記。<br />\n<br />\n早前，澳門特區郵電局局長劉惠明表示，法律生效後，手提電話用戶仍可自行購買預付卡，當激活電話卡時需於指定單位或手機應用程式實名登記，而於法律生效前使用中的預付卡需於 180天內完成實名登記手續，否則會被停止服務。<br />\n<br />\n澳門政府為配合《網絡安全法》生效，建議一份《修改司法警察局》法律草案，將涉及資訊網絡安全和國家安全犯罪列入司警權限。司警局將新增保安廳、國家安全情報工作廳、國家安全罪案調查處、恐佈主義罪案預警及調查處等特定附屬單位。行政長官可豁免公布這些特定司警人員晉升、開考、任用等名單，原因是他們的工作涉及跟蹤犯罪分子，或部分工作內容慣常需秘密偵查，希望可保障他們人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n網站全文：<a href=\"https://businessdigest.io/post/1440/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessdigest.io%2Fpost%2F1440%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt85zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=24bc12f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessdigest.io/post/1440/</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; <br />\n上網實名登記"},{"pid":"1b780bdc879e5796b2bfc780e7cfec81205a222a","tid":1744024,"uid":49151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"澳門市"},{"pid":"722a06f566935d0fb7ac549d831f52a8bbd4383e","tid":1744024,"uid":124711,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"澳門真係好撚廢"},{"pid":"b06be7e9c11173e9d22570b6b5515d16269a3ba2","tid":1744024,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt85zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=7900935c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt85zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=0109b82b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt85zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=1ec71cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt85zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=1d0239ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efb0658fd52170b87b2600772b67685c3b4a6a0e","tid":1744024,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"每年一萬蚊嘅代價"},{"pid":"9da817c126ac9a4fb0f1fb97ddd8bda77035eadc","tid":1744024,"uid":170297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523751265e02b4f9b717bbb28ab57a29392206c3","tid":1744024,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b780bdc879e5796b2bfc780e7cfec81205a222a","tid":1744024,"uid":49151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"澳門市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"澳門村"},{"pid":"30d0a92a8ada9cc958d6b7a0952805478381434e","tid":1744024,"uid":316224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"唔反抗嘅後果！<br />\n傻鳩澳門羊"},{"pid":"33709051d21c79ab8241defcd85b3ed4127fe052","tid":1744024,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d28d2225095d35b7dbe39930b449330c9d5f44c","tid":1744024,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:11:27.000Z","msg":"中国廣東省珠海市澳門區"}]}